            p View presentations on best practices, specific use cases, and more.
            a.button(href='/webinars') Visit Webinars
        .col-md-3.col-xs-12.no-float.no-top.no-left
          .inner
            h5.careers-four-icon-li__header
              span.fa.fa-graduation-cap(aria-hidden='true')
              | Academy
            p
              | The Academy features resources to grow your program and expand your knowledge of the Dynamic Signal platform.
            a.button(href='/academy') Visit Academy
