            p A developer oriented resource for using the Dynamic Signal Product API.
            a.button(href='https://dev.voicestorm.com/') Visit API Docs
        .col-md-3.col-xs-12.no-float.no-top.no-bottom.no-right.no-left
          .inner
            h5.careers-four-icon-li__header
              span.fa.fa-file-archive-o(aria-hidden='true')
              | Release Notes
            p Keep track of new features and bug fixes.
            a.button(href='https://dynamicsignal.com/academy/#ufh-c-276132-release-notes') Visit API Docs
